{"tid":155113,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(字海多圖)有冇手足睇過救世之繭  咩評價？入黎傾下","createTime":"2017-03-13T18:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T10:11:43.000Z","uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8710c46386a9466dc2b243c283b58d1c7ceeafe","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:49:45.000Z","msg":"作者原來係聖槍修女個作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我用左兩晚時間睇曬成套野 <br />\n因為已經有end唔洗等更新好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故事我覺得算係我近年見過既算係完整程度冇得彈<br />\n一開始以為係王道野(當然都有好多熱血位)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事開頭比主角執翻黎隻loli萌到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢套野對男女主角+奈奈既刻畫真係冇得輸<br />\n男主：<br />\n以為係一般弱受男主..點知其實算係心懷鬼胎甚至全個故事最黑係佢..想利用奈奈果下真係睇到好嬲都好多內心戲 好好睇<br />\n太多感動位 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/14/024531_7e3a9ae8eff90c32e4a8dc3a20b06e56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F14%2F024531_7e3a9ae8eff90c32e4a8dc3a20b06e56.jpg&h=3da2966a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXth51o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXth51o.jpg&h=7d49538c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/14/024616_e0d57a91b1de177f2eaeaa396a9ffb1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F14%2F024616_e0d57a91b1de177f2eaeaa396a9ffb1a.jpg&h=bb4b5eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oc5P7dY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOc5P7dY.jpg&h=c4577c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/14/024919_a5ca8f07e510f634f8c6807ab9221c65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F14%2F024919_a5ca8f07e510f634f8c6807ab9221c65.jpg&h=d140792f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00eaa0e839875a2236a3491bb4bc10ebdd7ffd22","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca0701b171ad63dfc88baaf2e0b8fa44adc9c626","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"冇人睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"5d8680fe8a53ee57a1e6cffccc09f469948a8901","tid":155113,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"算完得幾好，但係聖槍好睇d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1858ca8a5db6d6aef9f4edf62a24346e8759ea30","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算完得幾好，但係聖槍好睇d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聖槍漫畫冇睇過..淨係有睇動畫個end<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聖槍可以話係sad到爆"},{"pid":"734fd5634d769681ee211986b8830d2977fd5e9f","tid":155113,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"女主角唔係奈奈？"},{"pid":"ebcb0bdc8a8dcd088db4aab519e9f72a333131ca","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女主角唔係奈奈？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蕾娜"},{"pid":"df66a852bbf96b41ea5bbc6664b0b7a038fd261d","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女主角唔係奈奈？</blockquote><br />\n 第三張圖男主攬住果個黑頭髮女仔"},{"pid":"a04d08ccee02f254f74a3252129d152f3b2793dd","tid":155113,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"個時連載住睇又隔得耐先一話成日唔記得之前講乜<br />\n主角似壞唔壞<br />\n最後條女都係ipad"},{"pid":"ba2af8df9231cce73982cb490552fa17f5173087","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個時連載住睇又隔得耐先一話成日唔記得之前講乜<br />\n主角似壞唔壞<br />\n最後條女都係ipad</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主角係果d失去左先知道咩係最重要(奈奈)<br />\n後期交代左好多背景<br />\n女主既過去比想像中仲要癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8663af24ff15d48d1b85eb868482d6a37f9f3543","tid":155113,"uid":89194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"本來追緊連載果陣預左佢爛尾<br />\n點知結局好完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d704e8c95657843b44ca6deb72921a257960beba","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本來追緊連載果陣預左佢爛尾<br />\n點知結局好完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得真係一套故事好好好完整既一部漫畫<br />\nd角色性格特色好正<br />\n<br />\n結局真係睇到有笑有淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3a4f6e8c96c15a70b27c53a43fbacc1c01e6c5","tid":155113,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}